author: @patwalker5133
text: I have been so happy for Jin's during his solo time in the spotlight, but I have also been so worried too. It seems he has been going nonstop since his discharge. He never seemed to have a moment to catch his breath. Now, we have J-Hope back to help represent the other members while they finish their service.  A load shared is easier to carry.  I think Jin was just as happy as everyone else. He was so helpful in making J-Hope exit as smooth as possible. I hope they have a bull-session later with some good food and shared some stories of their similar experience in the military. Later, I hope J-Hope sneaks down to his old dance studio and decompresses. Either way, welcome Home J-Hope!!! 💜💜💜💜💜💜💜
